<HL>
   Exxon Faces U.S. Suit
   Over Small Oil Spills
   In New Jersey Waters
</HL>
<DATE>
04/13/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   XON
