WSJ900413-0059
</DOCNO>
<DOCID>
900413-0059.
</DOCID>
<HL>
   Business Brief -- Automatic Data Processing Inc.:
   Quarterly Profit Rose 16%
   On Revenue Increase of 4%
</HL>
<DATE>
04/13/90
</DATE>
<SO>
